"Materials" means the software, scripts, notebooks, documentation, data
summaries, molecular candidate lists, computational readouts, figures, reports,
and other research artifacts contained in this repository.

"Non-Commercial Research Use" means personal, academic, internal laboratory, or
non-commercial evaluation use that does not generate revenue, support a paid
service, form part of a commercial product, support patent prosecution, or
support clinical, diagnostic, therapeutic, procurement, synthesis, or wet-lab
testing activity without separate written permission.

